snippet.title: Goose Simulator - ALPHA 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
ALPHA 1 will be the first publicly playable version of the game. We have tested it but there are definitely still game-breaking glitches we need to fix. We are planning on leaving in most glitches to make the game hilarious but we need to remove some of them to make the game playable. We are planning on having 3-5 Alpha Versions before the full release which could be as early as The end of June to as late as The end of October or November.

Have you ever wanted to roam around a Cartoon City and shoot things, blow crap up and go flying through the air at uncontrollable speeds? Well, you are in for a treat because that is what Goose Simulator is all about! Worst game physics ever, got em. 100s of Dumb glitches, got em. Hilariously Stupid Story mode, got it. Jump into Goose Sim This Summer.

Goose Simulator ItchIO Page: https://donquae-alfred.itch.io/goosesimulator

Donquae Alfred Itch. io Page: https://donquae-alfred.itch.io

Twitter: https://twitter.com/DonquaeAlfred

Website: https://sites.google.com/view/donquae...

Contact: "donquaealfred@gmail.com" is our Contact Email
